      • testMapTupleFromMetadata

        public void testMapTupleFromMetadata()
        Test a complex map schema of the form:
        a.`b.x`.`c.y`.d
        in which columns "a", "b.x" and "c.y" are maps, "b.x" and "c.y" are names that contains dots, and d is primitive. Here we build up the schema using the metadata schema, and generate a materialized field from the metadata.
